WEBVTT

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.000
IF I CAN'T PASS ANYTHING?
I CAN'T DO ANYTHING.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Announcer: WE ALL WANT
 OUR CHILDREN TO DO WELL.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.000
BUT WHAT HAPPENS WHEN THEY
 JUST CAN'T SEEM TO LEARN?

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Man: IT'S VERY DIFFICULT
 FOR YOU TO WATCH YOUR CHILD

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.000
NOT WANT TO DO SOMETHING

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:30.000
THAT YOU HAVE TO
MAKE THEM DO EVERY DAY.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.000
AND THAT'S WHAT SCHOOL
WAS BECOMING, IT WAS A BATTLE.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Announcer: TODAY,
 A LAST-CHANCE SCHOOL

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:37.000
FOR KIDS WITH
 LEARNING PROBLEMS.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:38.000
IS THIS PROPER?

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:41.000
AND NEW FINDINGS ABOUT HOW
 YOU CAN HELP YOUR OWN CHILD.

