LAST YEAR'S TEACHER
WAS TO GET ON HER BACK,

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.000
THIS YEAR'S TEACHER
SAID "LEAVE HER ALONE."

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.000
OBVIOUSLY YOU ARE
UNDER A LOT OF PRESSURE.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:52.000
Announcer:
 BRAZELTON ON PARENTING.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.000
( theme music playing )

